{"tid":2449993,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉旺角站出口縱火 青年暴動罪成還柙候判","createTime":"2021-03-17T05:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T08:20:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d513d7507e7b640d60054f8a12ab8b7073caa975","tid":2449993,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14448&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=9b0b4db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14448</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭<br />\n#祁士偉法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n👤沈(19) #1103旺角<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：暴動<br />\n被控於2019年11月3日，在旺角彌敦道及亞皆老街附近參與暴動。<br />\n==================<br />\n被告人正式答辯：<br />\n控罪1：認罪🛑<br />\n控罪2和3：不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n因被告人承認控罪1，基於認罪協議，控方不會起訴控罪2和3，即「縱火」和「身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品」。<br />\n==================<br />\n📌被告人在本案的作為：<br />\n-參與暴動<br />\n-用黑布遮面<br />\n-把垃圾放在馬路上的火堆<br />\n-把木卡板和發泡膠放在旺角站C1出口的火堆<br />\n-把雜物踢入在旺角站C1出口的火堆<br />\n==================<br />\n📌求情：<br />\n辯方律師指出被告願意在今天賠償約$100400的港鐵維修費用。律師指出被告人已明白控罪嚴重，第一時間認罪已是最有力的求情理由。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師指出被告沒有案底，生於破碎家庭，但他未有因此放棄，在他被捕後，有一直參與義工活動，例如照顧老人服務等；亦有捐血習慣；為了照顧年邁的祖父母，一直半工讀，並把一半的收入作為家用。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師亦已指出被告人因本案已上了一課，當時沒有使用攻擊性武器，沒有令警員受傷，案發時只有20-30人在現場，規模較小，被告亦只是受他人影響而作出縱火行為，而不是他本人的原有性格。綜合以上，律師希望法庭可以在判刑前為被告索取一系列報告。<br />\n==================<br />\n法庭將案件會押至2021年3月31日1000進行判刑🛑期間會為需要還押看管的被告人索取背景和教導所報告🛑"},{"pid":"87554feeff58b3543ea482e18256814bd5cabadc","tid":2449993,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88689975bac0f82da7bb8667871887d7c6f05134","tid":2449993,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4adf9f55baa123f630e16967201105d541e263b","tid":2449993,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6932a5aa10549e90d6db7afc143ceaa4ec28342","tid":2449993,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4adf9f55baa123f630e16967201105d541e263b","tid":2449993,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2d4b3da23333b0346d1d0038132622c34d25df","tid":2449993,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88689975bac0f82da7bb8667871887d7c6f05134","tid":2449993,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<im